{
  "stem": "11274.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They are using sticks to get you off the bed if you can't wake up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they're beating you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is another reason that I didn't want to be a block elder, or a room elder-- I couldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I wasn't going to be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't beaten very often because I was alert and awake.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the minute I woke up, I pulled my sister down, and she was next to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So everything that I could.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remembered the words that I promised Mama, take care of your younger sister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Take care of [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did as much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she cooperated very nicely with everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And being that she was the youngest child and spoiled and babied and favored, I'm amazed how she could go through everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whatever happened-- scabies, or later on malaria-- she had it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have the scabies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a little bit itching on fingers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She had it on her whole body.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had to sell the portion of bread to get some salve to save her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, later on, they were choosing-- in Auschwitz, they were choosing, Mengele was mostly the one choosing for different details.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had- I knew only that Mengele had details, different kinds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was choosing for other jobs, too, and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- what I--and I saw people, while we were marching out, other people, other girls, like us, in the same-- and he had the white apron with them, wearing, too.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Were going somewhere, doing something under the SS and under the kapo, doing something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they looked terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were skinny, and their eyes were dead, just practically holes looking at it when we passed them by.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
